            "twoColumn": "校园文学联盟",
            "list": [
                {
                    "id": "242",
                    "isNewRecord": false,
                    "remarks": "",
                    "createDate": "",
                    "updateDate": "",
                    "title": "就诊记",
                    "summary": "近日行车不慎，不幸负伤。右脚小趾剧烈形变，又红又肿，还好书报满屋，很容易便从中缝广告内挖出了一家自称是“专家主治，服务优良”的医院。",
                    "author": "文/榆林十中八年级一班高阳",
                    "recUnit": "青少年宫",
                    "contact": "",
                    "relDate": "2016-08-31",
                    "magaImgurl": "|/magazine/userfiles/files/mag/mgMagazine/2016/11/15.jpg",
                    "magaLogourl": "|/magazine/userfiles/files/mag/mgMagazine/2016/10/aaa(1).jpg",
                    "firstColumn": "青春在线",
                    "twoColumn": "校园文学联盟",
                    "periodicalDate": "2016-08",
                    "state": "",
                    "periodical": "103",
                    "content": "<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">近日行车不慎，不幸负伤。右脚小趾剧烈形变，又红又肿，还好书报满屋，很容易便从中缝广告内挖出了一家自称是&ldquo;专家主治，服务优良&rdquo;的医院。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">真不愧是&ldquo;服务优良&rdquo;！医院不大，大堂正对着门贴了张奇大的宣传画&mdash;&mdash;手捧鲜花的白衣天使面带微笑，上面写了一排字，&ldquo;优质服务，真情奉献&rdquo;。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">我一瘸一拐去了挂号处，方才&ldquo;白衣天使&rdquo;的良好形象，却突然被一个个面若冰霜，毫无表情的护士小姐彻底抹杀。递过钱，换了张半透明的挂号单后，就休想再提半个问题，否则答案也都是不折不扣的三个字&ldquo;自己看&rdquo;。回到大堂，又看到宣传画上那满面春光的白衣天使，真有些莫名其妙。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">才到三楼骨科，羊肠一般的过道早已拥挤不堪，待进了候诊室，方才惊叹人体本身潜能之巨大。不过是十平方米的地方，挤得是蚊蝇不入。况且这都是些断腿折臂、捂腰拄杖之辈。固任我发挥昔日跑食堂之绝技，毕竟外挤内伤，最终亦无一丝作用。还好并非只身独往，母亲只好钻过人墙，终于颤巍巍地递上了病例。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">两三个小时过去了，听说骨科早已停止挂号，就诊室内也渐渐清净下来。大好光阴如此耗费，对欲求医治病的人来说，只怕没病也要等出毛病来，小病也会等成大病吧。还好未见有颈椎断者，否则恐怕还未及就诊，就早已一命呜呼了！</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">有人谓看病有&ldquo;一长一短&rdquo;，果然，候诊时间之长，使我已近睡梦。突然耳畔响起了默诵了几百遍的挂号数字，神经元一时兴奋，做了个极不雅致的动作。但还未激动，却已被众人的纷纷侧目所打败。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">一跛一跳地进了就诊室，屁股未沾椅，专家便令脱去鞋袜，两指一捏一揉，问了声痛否，便开始提笔疾书。半面病历几秒便已绘完，但我却花了十多分钟也猜不出一字，含蓄地向专家提问，结果却唯有三个字，&ldquo;去拍片&rdquo;。专家就是专家，三个字扩展了半页病例，妙！</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">忙了好一阵，一小时后又回到就诊室，躺上了病床。但见专家把</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">X</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">光片对光一瞅，一排指头便开始在小趾上揉搓，借助身体重力猛压一下，微微一震，便说已对我进行了回位手术，接着又对我说了一通到</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">XX</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">交钱，再到</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">XX</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">领药，再于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">XX</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">返回复查</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">XX</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">脚还在余痛，我的大脑信息接收器还未打开，便又得二字&ldquo;去吧&rdquo;！到楼下拿药，恍惚间被专家细致周到的服务大为震动。一大堆药片全为一根脚趾。从抹得到吃的，从维生素到抗生素，从止痛片到钙片，几大张钞票也随之而逝。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">打道回府，又看见宣传栏上的&ldquo;白衣天使&rdquo;和那句&ldquo;优质服务</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">,</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">真情奉献&rdquo;，真不由得苦苦一笑。（指导老师：王红艳）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>",
                    "magaThumburl": "/magazine/userfiles/_thumbs/files/mag/mgMagazine/2016/08/15.jpg,",
                    "count": "",
                    "souCount": "",
                    "souName": "团市委各部室及下属单位"
                },
                {
                    "id": "243",
                    "isNewRecord": false,
                    "remarks": "",
                    "createDate": "",
                    "updateDate": "",
                    "title": "念",
                    "summary": "我是一个住在江南的孩子，我是一个离开家的孩子，我是一个家在远方，人在路上的孩子。",
                    "author": "文／榆林学院文学院汉语言文学专业陶鑫荣",
                    "recUnit": "青年服务中心",
                    "contact": "",
                    "relDate": "2016-08-31",
                    "magaImgurl": "|/magazine/userfiles/files/mag/mgMagazine/2016/11/16.jpg",
                    "magaLogourl": "|/magazine/userfiles/files/mag/mgMagazine/2016/10/aaa(1).jpg",
                    "firstColumn": "青春在线",
                    "twoColumn": "校园文学联盟",
                    "periodicalDate": "2016-08",
                    "state": "",
                    "periodical": "103",
                    "content": "<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">一纸千家墨，半世离人忧。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">举目隔江望，烟波最人愁。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&mdash;&mdash;题记</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">我是一个住在江南的孩子，我是一个离开家的孩子，我是一个家在远方，人在路上的孩子。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">江南夜色，塞北狂沙，本来是毫无瓜葛的两个地方却因为一场高考，因为一次选择而深深联系。我早已习惯了江南的温婉，习惯了江南的恬美，可因为那次选择，在那一天，我踏上了北去的列车，离开家乡，远赴一场塞北的约。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">朋友，留在家乡。家人，仍在家乡。而我，远在他乡。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">一友百人觅，十年醉花阴</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">忘记了夜晚偷懒的星星什么时候悄悄溜进了云层，却忘不了流星雨下，我们虔诚许下的诺言。远方的你们，还好吗？</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">时光将一切回忆都催化成人世间最美的毒药，而你我都是中毒至深的人。我们，曾坐在一起，高谈阔论，无视天高地厚。年前，我们笃信地许下一生一起走的诺言，虽然我们都清楚的知道那无非是痴人说梦。美好的东西总是很快就会消失。六月，似乎就是一个为一切事物画上句号的季节。当楼下四溢着栀子花香的时候，甜蜜与苦涩交织在了一起。我们嗅着花香，分享彼此年少最后的心事，因为，我们明白，那场做了三年的梦，就要醒了。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">学校，总是在那个时刻，刻意压抑着我们的情绪，努力将我们所有的心思投入到学习，投入到高考。的确，那是我们这一生比较重要的一次机会。朋友，话仿佛突然就少了，偶尔谈几句也脱不了高考的话题，可是，离别的愁绪早已酝酿，在心底悄然发芽。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">七月了，时间偷走了我们在一起的最后一个月。茶凉酒寒，曲终人散。我们像炸开的蒲公英四散在天地，说出口的再见，是再次相见，还是再也不见。离别的情书，我一封封堆叠着，留在时光深处，煽情的话语明明练习了好多遍，却仍没有说出口。我们就这么走了，就这么散了。现在，我伏案，脑海有你，有他，还有她。你们像是我早已定时好播放的电影，在离别后的今天，一幕幕呈现。是的，我承认，我是想你们了！离开家的时候，我将所有人的祝福都带着，满满的一个本子。在这，夜深的时候，我总会翻起，看那些熟悉的字体，细细念想。朋友，我想你们了，在远方，都好好的！</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">游子行八方，家母念归乡</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&ldquo;家里都好吧！&rdquo;这是我来这问父母的第一个问题。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">来这之后，和父母通话过几次，聊的都是一些家常，对于其他的话题我们彼此好像都不会轻易去寻找，去触及。父母今年四十过半了，劳累了半生，青丝也已蹿上了他们的头上。从南方到北方，千里之遥，行途和生活的衣物是母亲整理的。临行前的那个晚上，母亲在我的房间一件一件叠着我的衣物，嘴里仿佛有说不完的话。当房间里的闹钟不自觉地指向了零点，母亲却丝毫没有察觉，她不住的重复着&ldquo;那边干，要记得多喝水&rdquo;&ldquo;那边冷，不要在乎衣服好不好看，多穿几件&hellip;&hellip;&rdquo;星光折进窗台，她的青丝被照的分明。时光缝隙，有泪珠的痕迹。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">我不是一个特别恋家的孩子，这和父亲很相似。父亲</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">18</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">岁便离开了家，和叔叔一起外出务工，所以，他的性格似乎总是透露着刚毅，不管是真实的，还是伪装的。那天，录取通知下来的时候，当他得知我将要离开家，去向千里之外的时候，他先是怔了一下，然后站起身，默默走到走廊处，手扶在墙上，头靠在手上，失声痛哭。那是我这二十年第一次见他哭。他喃喃&ldquo;我就这么一个儿子，却要一个人去那么远的地方&hellip;&hellip;&rdquo;虚掩了二十年的坚强顷刻间倒塌，父亲，那个深爱我的人，哭了！</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">我在这，家里人的心一半在家，一半在这。我的心剧烈地颤抖了一下，思乡的心弦被猛地拨动，震耳欲聋，久不停息。我想起了父母，想起了亲人，想起了那个我生活了二十年的地方。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">呵，亲爱的人啊！远方的距离虽然遥远，但是，我们的心是连在一起的，这，无关距离。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">举目隔江望，烟波最人愁</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">念，一种简单的情感，可当你念着的时候，你的世界却是复杂的。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">我的夜晚，我念的情结像一曲旧音，遥寄我最深的念想。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>",
                    "magaThumburl": "/magazine/userfiles/_thumbs/files/mag/mgMagazine/2016/08/16.jpg,",
                    "count": "",
