                    "title": "《白鹿原》的茅盾文学奖之路",
                    "summary": "1995年秋，第四届茅盾文学奖开评，《白鹿原》成为绕不过的一部长篇",
                    "author": "文／李清霞",
                    "recUnit": "青工农部",
                    "contact": "",
                    "relDate": "2016-08-31",
                    "magaImgurl": "|/magazine/userfiles/files/mag/mgMagazine/2016/10/8.jpg",
                    "magaLogourl": "|/magazine/userfiles/files/mag/mgMagazine/2016/10/aaa(1).jpg",
                    "firstColumn": "青春在线",
                    "twoColumn": "青春专栏",
                    "periodicalDate": "2016-08",
                    "state": "",
                    "periodical": "103",
                    "content": "<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">1995</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">年秋，第四届茅盾文学奖开评，《白鹿原》成为绕不过的一部长篇，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">10</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">月底评出</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">20</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">部初选作品，《白鹿原》在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">23</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">人专家审读小组顺利通过。却不知什么原因停止了终评，直到时过两年才进行评选。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">著名评论家陈涌反复琢磨作品，然后在评委会上拿出正式意见</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">,</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">即两个基本上：&ldquo;作品在政治上基本没有问题；作品在性描写上基本没有问题。&rdquo;评委会意见基本达成一致。陈涌还著长文《关于陈忠实的创作》，对陈忠实的文学创作进行了客观科学系统的论述和评价。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">他认为&ldquo;陈忠实从他</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">70</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">年代发表小说开始，便一直是一个接续过去现实主义传统的作家，他还很少受到其他艺术方法的影响。&rdquo;《白鹿原》则让我们看到，陈忠实&ldquo;充分地理解现实斗争的复杂性，理解中国革命的长期性、复杂性和残酷性这个特点，但又同样清楚地看到中国历史发展的趋向。&rdquo;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">文章最后指出：&ldquo;尽管陈忠实在自己探索中国社会关系和社会斗争的过程中，也出现了自己主观认识上的一些问题，但他整体思想倾向的正确是应该肯定的，他的这部作品，深刻地反映了解放前中国的现实的真实，是主要的。&rdquo;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">茅盾文学奖颁奖后的几天，陈忠实和白烨去拜访了陈涌老人，他告诉陈忠实，因为《白鹿原》的阅读使他对陈忠实的小说产生了兴趣，就自己到新华书店买了《陈忠实小说自选集》（华夏出版社</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">1996</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">年版）的短篇卷和中篇卷两本，约一百万字，读完后才写了那篇论文交给《文学评论》。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">陈忠实称陈涌为&ldquo;释疑者&rdquo;，陈涌认为《白鹿原》不存在&ldquo;历史倾向问题&rdquo;，让陈忠实&ldquo;知遇&rdquo;之外更由衷地&ldquo;钦敬&rdquo;。陈涌是我国著名的马克思主义文艺理论家。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">评委会提出了修改意见：作品中儒家文化的体现者朱先生这个人物关于政治斗争&ldquo;翻鏊子&rdquo;的评论，以及与此有关的若干描写可能引出误会，应以适当的方式予以廓清；另外，一些与表现思想主题无关的较直露的性描写应加以删改。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">何启治认为，被删改的两处性描写，既是情节发展的需要，也是人物塑造的需要，应该保留才是。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">那以后，陈忠实每次到北京开会，只要有时间都去拜访陈涌老先生。陈涌不抽烟，他知道陈忠实喜欢抽雪茄后，有朋友从国外回来送他雪茄，他就攒着，转送给陈忠实。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">2015</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">10</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">21</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">日，陈涌老先生追思会，陈忠实因病未能出席，他特意打电话给白烨，请白烨&ldquo;将他对陈涌的深切缅怀和崇高的敬意带到会上&rdquo;。陈忠实说他对陈涌永远感念，并说陈涌&ldquo;对我和我的创作的支持是至关重要的&rdquo;。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">2005</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">6</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">月，陈忠实做客《艺术人生》，朱军问起此事，陈忠实说当时是评委会的同志给他去的电话，他答应修改前还明确问过，是不是只有修改了才有参评资格。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">评委会的同志明确地回答，评委会的意见已经基本一致，修改不修改都获奖；建议修改，只是为了作品本身更完美而已。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">当年《白鹿原》第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">次印数是</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">14850</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">册，到同年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">10</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">月第七次印刷，累计印数</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">56</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">万多册。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">2008</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">9</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">月，中国作家协会副主席张炯在接受徐州师范大学学报访问时说：&ldquo;我觉得，一些茅盾文学奖的获奖作品在不久的将来也会成为经典，比如说陈忠实的《白鹿原》、张洁的《无字》等。我认为《无字》可以成为女性文学的经典。&rdquo;随后，他谈到</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">1998</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">年在瑞典斯德哥尔摩访问时与马悦然会谈的情况。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">他说两人在斯德哥尔摩大学会面，交谈了很长时间，马悦然向他推荐了自己喜欢的好作品，包括高行健的戏剧、李锐的《旧址》等，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">2000</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">年高行健以《灵山》等作品荣获诺贝尔文学奖。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">他也向马悦然推荐了国内近年来的好作品，其中包括《白鹿原》，马悦然说他还没有读过《白鹿原》，张炯就将随身携带的《白鹿原》送给了他。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>",
                    "magaThumburl": "/magazine/userfiles/_thumbs/files/mag/mgMagazine/2016/08/8.jpg,",
                    "count": "",
