                    "state": "",
                    "periodical": "103",
                    "content": "<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">7</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">6</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">日，榆林市青年企业家协会第二次会员代表大会在榆召开。团省委书记段小龙，市人大常委会副主任麻宝玉，副市长杨东明，市政协副主席贾正兰、苗丰出席大会，市委副书记高中印讲话，省青年企业家协会会长崔程致辞。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">会议听取并审议通过了《榆林市青年企业家协会第一届理事会工作报告（草案）》《榆林市青年企业家协会第一届理事会财务收支情况报告（草案）》《榆林市青年企业家协会章程修正案（草案）》，选举产生了第二届理事会、常务理事、会长、常务副会长、副会长、秘书长等。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">高中印在讲话中对榆林市青年企业家协会的工作给予充分肯定。他指出，榆林有良好的发展基础、巨大的发展空间、难得的政策机遇，经济社会发展潜力大、希望大、舞台大，仍然处于大有可为的重要战略机遇期。青年企业家要领会新要求、把握新定位，认真学习习近平总书记&ldquo;七一&rdquo;重要讲话精神，用讲话精神武装头脑、指导实践，坚定不移跟党走。要树立新理念、实现新开局，认真研读政策文件，密切关注政策走势，紧紧围绕五大发展理念谋发展、促转型。要适应新常态、增添新干劲，一起研判大势、集思广益、抱团发展，促进企业在&ldquo;十三五&rdquo;平稳发展。要进入新状态、奋力新作为，正视困难，坚定信心，爬坡过坎，带头抓好创新转型、带头推进开放合作、带头重构诚信体系、带头履行社会责任。青年企业家协会要坚持服务第一原则，巩固纽带作用，对接关键资源，提供服务平台，不断创新服务内容，改进工作方式，为榆林发展吸纳更多要素、拓展更广空间。各级各部门要强化组织领导，优化政务环境，营造良好氛围，一如既往地支持青年企业家发展。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">会上，榆林市青年企业家协会为驻北京、上海、深圳、西安分会授牌，并为北京歌剧舞剧院国家一级演员、青年歌唱家王二妮颁发了艺术顾问聘书。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>",
                    "magaThumburl": "/magazine/userfiles/_thumbs/files/mag/mgMagazine/2016/08/33.jpg,",
                    "count": "",
                    "souCount": "",
                    "souName": "团市委各部室及下属单位"
                },
                {
                    "id": "264",
                    "isNewRecord": false,
                    "remarks": "",
                    "createDate": "",
                    "updateDate": "",
                    "title": "共青团榆林市委圆满完成陕西省青少年 社会抽样调查榆林市调查督导工作",
                    "summary": "根据团省委统一部署，团市委在6—7月份对市内部分小学生、初中生、高中生、",
                    "author": "",
                    "recUnit": "办公室",
                    "contact": "",
                    "relDate": "2016-08-31",
                    "magaImgurl": "|/magazine/userfiles/files/mag/mgMagazine/2016/11/34.jpg",
                    "magaLogourl": "|/magazine/userfiles/files/mag/mgMagazine/2016/10/aaa(1).jpg",
                    "firstColumn": "青春在线",
                    "twoColumn": "刊中报",
                    "periodicalDate": "2016-08",
                    "state": "",
                    "periodical": "103",
                    "content": "<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">根据团省委统一部署，团市委在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">6</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&mdash;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">7</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">月份对市内部分小学生、初中生、高中生、大学生、农村青年、党政事业单位青年、企业青年和社会组织青年等</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">8</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">类群体进行了抽样调查，圆满完成了陕西省青少年百分之一人口社会抽样调查榆林市调查督导工作。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">调研前，团市委召开专门会议部署调研工作，制定科学的调研方案，成立调研督导组，安排各班子成员亲自带队奔赴各县区开展督导。各县区团委精心筹备部署，积极沟通协调，使调查工作得到了有关党政机关、企事业单位、社会团体、学校和农村基层组织的积极配合。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">团市委督导组人员和各县区调查组人员密切配合，深入党政机关、工矿企业、学校组织、基层农村、社会团体，广泛宣传、耐心讲解，充分利用与基层青年直接交流的机会，宣讲中省市群团工作会议精神和团中央改革方案，听取青年心声，了解青年需求，共发放调查问卷</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">6300</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">份，收回有效问卷</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">5800</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">份。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">通过本次调研督导，使团市委更加全面、准确地掌握了全市青少年的基本状况，为下一步更好地发挥组织青年、引导青年、服务青年和维护青少年合法权益的作用，着力推动共青团改革发展，推动新常态下榆林共青团工作打下坚实的基础。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>",
                    "magaThumburl": "/magazine/userfiles/_thumbs/files/mag/mgMagazine/2016/08/34.jpg,",
                    "count": "",
                    "souCount": "",
                    "souName": "团市委各部室及下属单位"
                },
                {
                    "id": "265",
                    "isNewRecord": false,
                    "remarks": "",
                    "createDate": "",
                    "updateDate": "",
                    "title": "庆七一榆林市“蒙赛尔杯”中小学生严实品德教育 演讲比赛暨学校战线颁奖典礼圆满举行",
                    "summary": "高举团旗跟党走，奋力实现中国梦。",
                    "author": "",
                    "recUnit": "榆林高新区团委",
                    "contact": "",
                    "relDate": "2016-08-31",
                    "magaImgurl": "|/magazine/userfiles/files/mag/mgMagazine/2016/11/35.jpg",
                    "magaLogourl": "|/magazine/userfiles/files/mag/mgMagazine/2016/10/aaa(1).jpg",
                    "firstColumn": "青春在线",
                    "twoColumn": "刊中报",
                    "periodicalDate": "2016-08",
                    "state": "",
                    "periodical": "103",
                    "content": "<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">高举团旗跟党走，奋力实现中国梦。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">7</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">日上午，在纪念建党九十五周年之际，由团市委、市文明办、市教育局、市少工委主办的&ldquo;庆七一&middot;榆林市&lsquo;蒙赛尔杯&rsquo;中小学生严实品德教育演讲比赛&rdquo;在市委会议中心隆重举行。市人大常委会副主任马治东、市政协副主席杨志先等领导同志出席。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">团市委书记殷海舰发表了热情洋溢的致辞，他希望通过此次严实品德教育演讲比赛，全市广大青少年从自身做起，从小事做起，从严从实、向上向善&mdash;&mdash;争做榆林好少年。希望营造出广大青少年从严从实、向上向善的鲜明导向和浓厚氛围，引导全市广大青少年把&ldquo;严实&rdquo;要求融入日常规范，以严的标准、实的精神自觉培育践行社会主义核心价值观，为实现中国梦努力奋斗。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">决赛中，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">12</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">名参赛选手结合自身学习情况和身边典型事迹，用生动的语言和真挚的感情讲述自己努力在立志、修德、成才等方面以&ldquo;严&rdquo;的精神和&ldquo;实&rdquo;的品德要求自己，为我们带来了精彩的比赛。最终来自米脂县第三中学的霍惠芝同学获得中学组第一名，来自榆林市第一小学的梁好同学获得小学组第一名。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">?<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">比赛结束后，还进行了全市学校战线颁奖典礼，为全市</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">20</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">名&ldquo;最美青年教师&rdquo;以及&ldquo;最美中学（职）生&rdquo;、优秀团干部等代表颁奖。活动在全体与会人员齐声高唱&ldquo;没有共产党就没有新中国&rdquo;的歌声中结束。</span></p>",
                    "magaThumburl": "/magazine/userfiles/_thumbs/files/mag/mgMagazine/2016/08/35.jpg,",
                    "count": "",
                    "souCount": "",
                    "souName": "市直团工委"
                },
                {
                    "id": "266",
                    "isNewRecord": false,
                    "remarks": "",
                    "createDate": "",
                    "updateDate": "",
                    "title": "共青团榆林市委、市青年服务中心联合青年公益 组织为榆阳区小壕兔镇受灾儿童发放暴雨灾害救灾物资",
                    "summary": "7月9日，榆林市连降暴雨，导致部分县区发生洪涝灾害，其中榆阳区小壕兔镇灾情最为严重。",
                    "author": "",
                    "recUnit": "组宣部",
                    "contact": "",
                    "relDate": "2016-08-31",
                    "magaImgurl": "|/magazine/userfiles/files/mag/mgMagazine/2016/11/36.jpg",
                    "magaLogourl": "|/magazine/userfiles/files/mag/mgMagazine/2016/10/aaa(1).jpg",
                    "firstColumn": "青春在线",
                    "twoColumn": "刊中报",
                    "periodicalDate": "2016-08",
                    "state": "",
                    "periodical": "103",
                    "content": "<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">7</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">9</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">日，榆林市连降暴雨，导致部分县区发生洪涝灾害，其中榆阳区小壕兔镇灾情最为严重。在团市委和市青年服务中心的支持下，壹基金联合兴平城市应急救援队、陕西民间公益行动联盟、榆林市青少年社工协会，第一时间组织成员代表前往受灾地区进行灾情评估，并根据灾情评估信息在最快的时间内做出针对受灾儿童的紧急救援方案。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">为在灾情发生后的第一时间给孩子们送去关爱，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">7</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">12</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">日晚，联盟成员代表和志愿者对价值</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">8</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">万多元救援物资&mdash;&mdash;壹基金救灾&ldquo;温暖包&rdquo;进行了装车，并于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">13</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">日早晨紧急运到榆阳区小壕兔镇中心小学。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">7</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">13</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">日上午，共青团榆林市委、陕西民间公益行动联盟、榆林市青年服务中心、小壕兔镇人民政府、小壕兔镇中心小学将壹基金洪灾&ldquo;温暖包&rdquo;&mdash;&mdash;发放到了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">239</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">名受灾儿童手中。</span></p>",
                    "magaThumburl": "/magazine/userfiles/_thumbs/files/mag/mgMagazine/2016/08/36.jpg,",
                    "count": "",
                    "souCount": "",
                    "souName": "团市委各部室及下属单位"
                },
                {
                    "id": "267",
                    "isNewRecord": false,
                    "remarks": "",
                    "createDate": "",
                    "updateDate": "",
                    "title": "榆林市青少年宫创意绘画班 举办民俗文化户外写生夏令营",
                    "summary": "为了提高学员的艺术修养和审美能力，加强学院对素描绘画的掌握能力",
                    "author": "",
                    "recUnit": "办公室",
                    "contact": "",
                    "relDate": "2016-08-31",
                    "magaImgurl": "|/magazine/userfiles/files/mag/mgMagazine/2016/11/37.jpg",
                    "magaLogourl": "|/magazine/userfiles/files/mag/mgMagazine/2016/10/aaa(1).jpg",
                    "firstColumn": "青春在线",
                    "twoColumn": "刊中报",
                    "periodicalDate": "2016-08",
                    "state": "",
                    "periodical": "103",
                    "content": "<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">为了提高学员的艺术修养和审美能力，加强学院对素描绘画的掌握能力，让学员通过实践了解自然，学会在生活中寻找灵感和创意，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">7</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">24</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">日至</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">27</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">日，榆林市青少年宫创意绘画班的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">20</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">名优秀学员在佳县举办了为期四天的民俗文化户外写生夏令营活动。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">在活动中，孩子们走进了乡村最深处，在自然的环境中寻找和发现生活中的美景，用笔描绘出眼中的实景，表达了心中的美丽画卷。孩子们还欣赏了民俗文化历史实景演出，了解了当地的农耕，婚丧，人文，祭祀等风俗历史。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">通过这次民俗文化户外写生夏令营活动，学员们学习了专业技能，增加了生活知识，提高了孩子们的艺术修养和审美能力。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>",
                    "magaThumburl": "/magazine/userfiles/_thumbs/files/mag/mgMagazine/2016/08/37.jpg,",
                    "count": "",
                    "souCount": "",
                    "souName": "团市委各部室及下属单位"
                },
                {
                    "id": "268",
