                    "title": "榆林21家企业挂牌“新四板” 陕西股权 交易中心榆林企业挂牌孵化基地同步揭牌 胡志强段小龙出席尉俊东致辞",
                    "summary": "7月6日，我市首批21家企业通过陕西股权交易中心审核，在榆集中挂牌“新四板”。",
                    "author": "",
                    "recUnit": "市直团工委",
                    "contact": "",
                    "relDate": "2016-08-31",
                    "magaImgurl": "|/magazine/userfiles/files/mag/mgMagazine/2016/11/38.jpg",
                    "magaLogourl": "|/magazine/userfiles/files/mag/mgMagazine/2016/10/aaa(1).jpg",
                    "firstColumn": "青春在线",
                    "twoColumn": "刊中报",
                    "periodicalDate": "2016-08",
                    "state": "",
                    "periodical": "103",
                    "content": "<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">7</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">6</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">日，我市首批</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">21</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">家企业通过陕西股权交易中心审核，在榆集中挂牌&ldquo;新四板&rdquo;。陕西股权交易中心榆林企业挂牌孵化基地同步揭牌。市委书记胡志强、团省委书记段小龙、副市长张海峰出席，市长尉俊东致辞。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">挂牌仪式上，陕西金开贷金融服务有限公司、陕西汇鑫融资担保有限公司、榆林市青年企业家协会签订了三方关于陕西金开贷授信榆林青年企业家协会</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">5</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">亿元的战略合作协议。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">尉俊东在致辞中指出，&ldquo;十三五&rdquo;是榆林推进经济转型升级的关键期。市委、市政府认真落实中央新理念、新要求，提出了&ldquo;创新引领、主动转型&rdquo;的发展战略和打造&ldquo;三区一高地&rdquo;的奋斗目标。实现这样的奋斗目标面临着前所未有的挑战，迫切需要一批朝气蓬勃、富有理想、观念先进、敢打敢拼的新一代企业家，担当起引领和推动榆林民营经济转型升级的历史使命。希望广大青年企业家传承好老一代企业家的精神品质，坚定信心，抢抓机遇，迎难而上，在新的征途上创造新辉煌、谱写新篇章。要更加进取，更加开放，更加包容，更具学习意识，更具创新精神，更具社会责任感。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">尉俊东强调，榆林市青年企业家协会是党和政府联系青年企业家的桥梁和纽带，肩负着团结、引导、服务青年企业家的光荣任务。协会要进一步强化服务意识，创新服务方式，健全服务机制，不断增强自身的吸引力、凝聚力和影响力，努力把协会建成一个青年企业家相互交流、提高素质的家园，一个促进创业、实现价值的平台。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">陕西股权交易中心是陕西省政府批准设立的唯一指定股权交易托管机构，该交易中心自</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">2014</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">5</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">月正式揭牌运营以来，已形成了以企业挂牌、登记托管和投融资服务为核心的三大业务模块。截至目前，该中心发展各类会员</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">118</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">家，挂牌企业已达到</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">453</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">家，挂牌企业总股本为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">90</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">亿股。今后，该中心将充分利用&ldquo;孵化基地&rdquo;，对榆林的中小微企业进行筛选评估，不断拓宽榆林市中小企业投融资渠道、规范企业经营、提升企业形象、提高企业品牌知名度，增加企业信用等级、提高中小企业股权流动性、对接资本市场，促进企业尽快达到新三板、创业板、中小板和主板上市的要求将起到重要的作用。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">挂牌仪式后，张海峰副市长就如何运用金融资本服务企业发展作了讲座。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>",
                    "magaThumburl": "/magazine/userfiles/_thumbs/files/mag/mgMagazine/2016/08/38.jpg,",
                    "count": "",
                    "souCount": "",
                    "souName": "市直团工委"
                },
                {
                    "id": "269",
                    "isNewRecord": false,
                    "remarks": "",
                    "createDate": "",
                    "updateDate": "",
                    "title": "团省委书记段小龙来榆调研",
                    "summary": "7月4日至7日，团省委书记段小龙一行在榆林开展了为期4天的调研工作",
                    "author": "",
                    "recUnit": "办公室",
                    "contact": "",
                    "relDate": "2016-08-31",
                    "magaImgurl": "|/magazine/userfiles/files/mag/mgMagazine/2016/11/39.jpg",
                    "magaLogourl": "|/magazine/userfiles/files/mag/mgMagazine/2016/10/aaa(1).jpg",
                    "firstColumn": "青春在线",
                    "twoColumn": "刊中报",
                    "periodicalDate": "2016-08",
                    "state": "",
                    "periodical": "103",
                    "content": "<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">7</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">4</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">日至</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">7</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">日，团省委书记段小龙一行在榆林开展了为期</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">4</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">天的调研工作，团省委组织部部长谢小义、市委副秘书长冯光宏、团市委书记殷海舰陪同调研。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">调研组分别赴吴堡、横山、榆阳和子洲，就榆林共青团改革、精准扶贫、青年创业就业、青春驿站建设、少先队建设等工作开展调研，实地走访&ldquo;青年之声&middot;榆林&rdquo;平台、横山县永盛社区童梦空间、羊老大青年电商孵化中心，大象果园、子洲青春驿站、东关小学、三丰油脂厂等调研点。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">调研期间，段小龙参加了各界青年代表座谈会，传达《共青团中央改革方案》精神，细致解读改革重点内容。调研结束后，段小龙对榆林共青团工作予以充分肯定，并就今后工作提出四点要求：一是要紧扣去&ldquo;四化&rdquo;强&ldquo;三性&rdquo;的改革方向，就团中央已经明确的&ldquo;增强团的广泛性和代表性&rdquo;、&ldquo;直接联系、服务、引导青年的制度&rdquo;、&ldquo;增强团员先进性和光荣感&rdquo;的改革任务，认真抓好贯彻落实；二是要加强对全体辅导员和广大少先队员礼仪知识教育，不断强化其组织意识和组织荣誉感；三是要积极探索&ldquo;站企共建&rdquo;等青春驿站建设新模式，有效凝聚青年，面对面解决青年的问题与困难，尽最大努力把服务青年的各项举措落实到位；四是要创新思维、大力探索完善&ldquo;青年之声&rdquo;平台功能，做好示范引导，倾听青年心声、服务青年发展。</span></p>",
                    "magaThumburl": "/magazine/userfiles/_thumbs/files/mag/mgMagazine/2016/08/39.jpg,",
                    "count": "",
                    "souCount": "",
                    "souName": "团市委各部室及下属单位"
                },
                {
                    "id": "270",
                    "isNewRecord": false,
                    "remarks": "",
                    "createDate": "",
                    "updateDate": "",
                    "title": "共青团榆林市委举办“两学一做” 第二次专题学习讨论会",
                    "summary": "7月15日，团市委机关召开“两学一做”第二次专题学习讨论会。",
                    "author": "",
                    "recUnit": "榆阳区团委",
                    "contact": "",
                    "relDate": "2016-09-01",
                    "magaImgurl": "|/magazine/userfiles/files/mag/mgMagazine/2016/11/40.jpg",
                    "magaLogourl": "|/magazine/userfiles/files/mag/mgMagazine/2016/10/aaa(1).jpg",
                    "firstColumn": "青春在线",
                    "twoColumn": "刊中报",
                    "periodicalDate": "2016-08",
                    "state": "",
                    "periodical": "103",
                    "content": "<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">7</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">15</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">日，团市委机关召开&ldquo;两学一做&rdquo;第二次专题学习讨论会。机关全体党员参加了研讨，团市委副书记、市青联副主席刘江涛主持会议。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">讨论会上，与会党员根据党章党规和习近平总书记系列讲话，重点围绕&ldquo;讲规矩、有纪律&rdquo;，结合自身工作、学习实践，就&ldquo;讲规矩、有纪律&rdquo;的深刻内涵、重要意义和实践要求展开广泛论述。通过学习研讨，大家进一步深化了对&ldquo;讲规矩、有纪律&rdquo;的认识，在不断深入开展&ldquo;两学一做&rdquo;学习教育活动上统一了思想、凝聚了共识，达到了相互促进、共同提高的目的。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">团市委书记、党组书记殷海舰以&ldquo;如何做一名讲规矩、守纪律的党员干部&rdquo;为题，从&ldquo;为什么&rdquo;、&ldquo;是什么&rdquo;和&ldquo;怎么样&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">三个方面系统阐述了讲规矩、有纪律的历史意义、深刻内涵和行动指南。殷海舰强调，共青团党员干部要领导带头、全体推进、专题研讨、注重实效，做好&ldquo;学&rdquo;的文章；密切协调、团结合作、有效沟通、形成合力，做好&ldquo;合&rdquo;的文章；健全制度、扎紧&ldquo;笼子&rdquo;、注重执行、强化监督，做好&ldquo;立&rdquo;的文章。殷海舰指出，要认识和把握&ldquo;讲规矩、有纪律&rdquo;的内涵和要义，把做好新常态下共青团工作与学习教育紧密结合，把&ldquo;两学一做&rdquo;精神与弘扬党的优良传统紧密结合。要进一步提高学习的自觉性和主动性，深入学习党章党规，树立党章党规意识，强化&ldquo;四个意识&rdquo;，守纪律、讲规矩，高标准、严要求践行&ldquo;两学一做&rdquo;，积极投身共青团改革发展伟大的实践。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>",
                    "magaThumburl": "/magazine/userfiles/_thumbs/files/mag/mgMagazine/2016/09/40.jpg,",
                    "count": "",
                    "souCount": "",
                    "souName": "县区团委"
                },
                {
                    "id": "271",
                    "isNewRecord": false,
                    "remarks": "",
                    "createDate": "",
                    "updateDate": "",
                    "title": "我市成立全国首家地市级青少年发展基金会 高中印揭牌并讲话",
                    "summary": "8月22日，榆林市希望青少年发展基金会成立大会暨爱心助学金发放仪式在榆举行。",
                    "author": "",
                    "recUnit": "组宣部",
                    "contact": "",
                    "relDate": "2016-08-31",
                    "magaImgurl": "",
                    "magaLogourl": "|/magazine/userfiles/files/mag/mgMagazine/2016/10/aaa(1).jpg",
                    "firstColumn": "青春在线",
                    "twoColumn": "刊中报",
                    "periodicalDate": "2016-08",
                    "state": "",
                    "periodical": "103",
                    "content": "<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">8</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">22</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">日，榆林市希望青少年发展基金会成立大会暨爱心助学金发放仪式在榆举行。市委副书记、市委政法委书记高中印揭牌并讲话，市人大常委会副主任麻宝玉、副市长杨东明、市政协副主席麻占平，以及团省委希望办主任、省青少年发展基金会秘书长乌钢，全国著名青年歌唱家王二妮等出席大会。会议由共青团榆林市委党组书记、书记殷海舰主持。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">据了解，榆林市希望青少年发展基金会是我市首家登记设立的非公募基金会，也是由共青团发起成立的除省会城市和部分副省级城市外的全国首家地市级青少年发展基金会，基金会以&ldquo;通过资助服务、利益表达和社会倡导，帮助青少年提高能力，改善青少年成长环境&rdquo;为宗旨，将始终关注全市广大青少年发展事业，特别是家庭贫困、品学兼优学子的学习生活。同时，榆林青基会的成立也得到了社会各界爱心组织和个人的大力支持。其中，榆林能源集团捐资</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">100</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">万元，设立了榆林能源集团爱心助学基金；王二妮及团队捐资</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">20</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">万元，设立了王二妮爱心助学基金；市青年企业家协会捐资</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">20</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">万元等，募集捐款总额为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">300</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">万元。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">高中印在讲话中指出，榆林青基会要坚持社会化的道路，统筹整合各种资源，牢固树立良好的社会公信力，把青基会不断做大做强，持续健康发展，形成独特的品牌魅力和影响力。价值追求要得到社会认同，致力于解决青少年的教育问题，为脱贫攻坚贡献共青团的力量。服务产品要形成社会影响，结合榆林实际，注重推陈出新、创新产品。扶助效用要达到雪中送炭，实现扶助精准化，引发社会共鸣，把更多榆林企业家乃至外地企业和爱心人士的力量吸引过来、凝聚起来，把规范管理、强化监督贯彻始终，依法依规依章、公开公平公正办事。服务成本要压到低了再低，用最低的服务成本，及时、便捷、深入地将社会各方爱心送到最急需帮助的困难青少年中间。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">同时，会上还为全市</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">70</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">名二本以上家庭贫困大学新生和</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">40</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">名品学兼优的中小学生，分别一次性捐助助学金</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">3000</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">元和</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">1000</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">元，共计</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">25</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">万元。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>",
                    "magaThumburl": "",
                    "count": "",
                    "souCount": "",
                    "souName": "团市委各部室及下属单位"
                },
                {
                    "id": "272",
                    "isNewRecord": false,
                    "remarks": "",
                    "createDate": "",
                    "updateDate": "",
                    "title": "榆林市第十届青少年暑期 社会实践夏令营活动圆满结束",
                    "summary": "8月5日至8月8日，由共青团榆林市委、榆林市少工委主办，榆林市青少年宫承办的“实践体验快乐•学习成就梦想”2016年榆林市第十届青少年暑期社会实践夏令营活动圆满结束。",
                    "author": "",
                    "recUnit": "编辑部",
                    "contact": "",
                    "relDate": "2016-08-31",
                    "magaImgurl": "|/magazine/userfiles/files/mag/mgMagazine/2016/11/41.jpg",
                    "magaLogourl": "|/magazine/userfiles/files/mag/mgMagazine/2016/10/aaa(1).jpg",
                    "firstColumn": "青春在线",
                    "twoColumn": "刊中报",
                    "periodicalDate": "2016-08",
                    "state": "",
                    "periodical": "103",
                    "content": "<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">8</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">5</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">日至</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">8</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">8</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">日，由共青团榆林市委、榆林市少工委主办，榆林市青少年宫承办的&ldquo;实践体验快乐&middot;学习成就梦想&rdquo;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">2016</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">年榆林市第十届青少年暑期社会实践夏令营活动圆满结束。来自全市的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">45</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">名市级优秀少先队员、进城务工农民工子女在榆林青少年社会实践基地&mdash;&mdash;榆林市射击场开展了为期</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">4</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">天的暑期社会实践夏令营活动。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">8</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">5</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">日上午，共青团榆林市委书记殷海舰，榆林市少工委主任、总辅导员孟红军出席并参加开营仪式。在开营仪式上，团市委书记殷海舰表示，青少年暑期社会实践夏令营是引导广大青少年培育和践行社会主义核心价值观的有效途径，团市委、市少工委开展公益夏令营活动已坚持十年，确属不易，目前该活动已成为团市委、市少工委开展青少年工作的一大品牌。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">在为期四天的活动中，小营员们积极参与丰富多彩的社会实践活动。在射击场，进行军事素质拓展训练，体验基本军姿站立、行进、军体拳、实弹射击、真人</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">CS</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">对抗等，让孩子们通过实践体验军人生活。在补浪河女子治沙连，参观女子民兵治沙连展览馆，让孩子们了解在艰苦的环境下，女子治沙连发扬自强不息、艰苦奋斗的优良传统，用青春和汗水践行着不畏艰难、不怕吃苦的创业精神，矢志不移、奋斗不止的愚公精神，实干苦干、敢打硬仗的拼搏精神，以苦为乐、以苦为荣的革命乐观主义精神，公而忘私、甘愿牺牲的奉献精神，让孩子们在潜移默化中树立自觉培养艰苦奋斗品质的意识，真正体会了榆林治沙精神。同时参观预备役</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">423</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">团，了解部队基本情况，参观学习一些基本的军事装备和营地，让孩子们真正体验正规军事部队的生活。另外还组织了科技手工制作、急救知识培训、团队协作训练、篝火晚会、农家采摘等丰富多彩的活动，让孩子们亲身参与其中，既锻炼了动手能力、思维能力，更重要的是培养他们的意志，学会忍耐、专注、执着，要有拼搏的精神，树立坚持到底就是胜利的意志品质，最大限度地发扬团队合作精神。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-font-kerning:1.0pt;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;\r\nmso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">青少年暑期社会实践夏令营活动是团市委、市少工委贯彻落实习近平总书记在接见第七次全国少代会代表时作出的&ldquo;从小在实践中学习做人、学习立志、学习创造&rdquo;重要指示精神的具体举措，作为团市委、市少工委着力打造的重点工作品牌，让青少年通过亲身参与各种各样的体验活动，丰富暑期生活的同时提高他们的社会实践能力，促进青少年健康快乐成长。</span></p>",
                    "magaThumburl": "/magazine/userfiles/_thumbs/files/mag/mgMagazine/2016/08/41.jpg,",
                    "count": "",
                    "souCount": "",
                    "souName": "编辑部"
                },
                {
                    "id": "273",
