                    "title": "共青团榆阳区委深化 希望工程助力我区脱贫攻坚",
                    "summary": "8月10日，共青团榆阳区委会同榆阳区慈善协会、壳牌长北项目赴安崖办事处沙舍科村进行希望工程项目验收。",
                    "author": "",
                    "recUnit": "编辑部",
                    "contact": "",
                    "relDate": "2016-08-31",
                    "magaImgurl": "|/magazine/userfiles/files/mag/mgMagazine/2016/11/43.jpg",
                    "magaLogourl": "|/magazine/userfiles/files/mag/mgMagazine/2016/10/aaa(1).jpg",
                    "firstColumn": "青春在线",
                    "twoColumn": "刊中报",
                    "periodicalDate": "2016-08",
                    "state": "",
                    "periodical": "103",
                    "content": "<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">8</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">10</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">日，共青团榆阳区委会同榆阳区慈善协会、壳牌长北项目赴安崖办事处沙舍科村进行希望工程项目验收。此项目经团区委与壳牌长北项目积极协调，由壳牌长北项目出资</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">30</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">万元，用于沙舍科村</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">8.3</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">公里水泥道路建设。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">近年来，团榆阳区委发挥自身优势，积极协调壳牌长北项目出资</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">629</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">万元，实施乡村医生免费培训、农村希望卫生室和基础设施建设等项目进一步深化希望工程，助力该区在全市率先全面脱贫、率先实现全面小康。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>",
