                    "state": "",
                    "periodical": "103",
                    "content": "<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">7</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">29</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">日上午，靖边县召开县委统战和党的群团工作会议。会议全面贯彻落实中央、省委和市委统战工作和党的群团工作会议精神，总结和回顾前一阶段全县统战和群团工作，安排部署当前和今后一个时期全县统战和群团工作。会上县委常委、政法委书记邬晓君，县委常委、宣传部部长贺秉禄，县委常委、统战部部长刘钧分别作了统战和群团工作专题发言，县委副书记白春阳对统战和群团工作进行了全面安排部署，县委书记、县长刘维平主持会议并作了总结讲话。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">会议指出，抓好统战工作和党的群团工作，是我们党的两项重要工作，全县上下要深刻学习领会中省市统战和群团工作会议精神，努力把全县人民的积极性和创造性调动起来，为全面建成小康靖边、实现&ldquo;五大梦想&rdquo;，凝聚更大力量、做出更大贡献。一是要进一步提高对统战和党的群团工作的认识。实现&ldquo;十三五&rdquo;规划和&ldquo;五大梦想&rdquo;的宏伟目标，需要凝聚方方面面的意志、智慧和力量。要充分发挥统一战线联系广泛的作用</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">, </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">全力调动社会各阶层的积极性、主动性和创造性</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">, </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">努力为全县经济社会发展凝聚力量。二是要切实加强新形势下统战和党的群团工作。统战工作要进一步做好民主党派和无党派人士工作，做好党外知识分子工作，做好非公有制经济领域统战工作，做好民族宗教工作，做好港澳台海外统战工作。党的群团工作要健全群团组织，实现全面覆盖、有效覆盖；要强化硬件保障，做到有经费、有阵地；要优化服务方式，做到精准服务、多样化服务；要提升自身能力，做到自身过硬、依法依章。三是要加强党对统战和群团工作的领导。要进一步加强党对统战工作的领导，注重培养使用党外人士。要进一步加强党对群团工作的领导，严格落实党赋予的各项任务，充分发挥群团组织中的党组领导核心作用。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>",
                    "magaThumburl": "/magazine/userfiles/_thumbs/files/mag/mgMagazine/2016/08/44.jpg,",
                    "count": "",
                    "souCount": "",
                    "souName": "编辑部"
                },
                {
                    "id": "276",
                    "isNewRecord": false,
                    "remarks": "",
                    "createDate": "",
                    "updateDate": "",
                    "title": "绥德团县委、农商银行20余万元 资助135名高考贫困学生",
                    "summary": "8月25日上午，由共青团绥德县委、绥德农商银行、绥德广播电视台共同主办的“精准扶贫•爱心助学”——2016年圆梦助学金发放仪式在县委第二会议室隆重举行。",
                    "author": "",
                    "recUnit": "编辑部",
                    "contact": "",
                    "relDate": "2016-08-31",
                    "magaImgurl": "|/magazine/userfiles/files/mag/mgMagazine/2016/11/45.jpg",
                    "magaLogourl": "|/magazine/userfiles/files/mag/mgMagazine/2016/10/aaa(1).jpg",
                    "firstColumn": "青春在线",
                    "twoColumn": "刊中报",
                    "periodicalDate": "2016-08",
                    "state": "",
                    "periodical": "103",
                    "content": "<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">金风送爽，丹桂飘香。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"> 8</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">25</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">日上午，由共青团绥德县委、绥德农商银行、绥德广播电视台共同主办的&ldquo;精准扶贫&middot;爱心助学&rdquo;&mdash;&mdash;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">2016</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">年圆梦助学金发放仪式在县委第二会议室隆重举行。活动主办单位主要负责人及扶贫办、教育局相关负责人，受助学生、部分家长代表共计</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">160</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">人参加了仪式。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">仪式上，团县委书记刘政亮介绍了本次资助活动开展过程和受助学生的基本情况。绥德农商银行将</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">224000</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">元&ldquo;精准扶贫&middot;爱心助学&rdquo;捐赠支票转交团县委。与会领导为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">20</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">名受助学生代表发放了助学金。受助学生代表作了真诚的感恩发言，并向绥德农商银行赠送了&ldquo;爱心签字旗&rdquo;。绥德农商银行行长常建安在讲话中希望同学们坚定信念，树立远大理想，刻苦学习，早日成才；希望受助学生要常怀感恩之心，感恩社会、传递爱心；呼吁社会各界大力支持和积极参与爱心助学、扶贫帮困公益活动。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">本次活动资助的对象是</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">2016</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">年参加高考并被本科以上高校录取的绥德籍贫困家庭学生，得到了农商银行、广播电视台的鼎立支持。绥德农商银行共捐赠</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">22.4</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">万元，对</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">135</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">名符合救助条件的绥德籍贫困生进行资助。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">今后，共青团绥德县委、绥德农商银行将继续关注和帮扶贫困学子，动员和凝聚更多的社会力量参与到精准扶贫和帮困助学活动中来，切实为我县品学兼优的贫困家庭学生解决实际困难，为绥德县全面打好脱贫攻坚战贡献青春正能量。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>",
                    "magaThumburl": "/magazine/userfiles/_thumbs/files/mag/mgMagazine/2016/08/45.jpg,",
                    "count": "",
                    "souCount": "",
                    "souName": "编辑部"
                },
                {
                    "id": "277",
                    "isNewRecord": false,
                    "remarks": "",
                    "createDate": "",
                    "updateDate": "",
                    "title": "精彩文艺活动演绎别样童年",
                    "summary": "为了给小朋友们的暑期生活增添更多快乐的色彩，7月22日，由共青团府谷县委主办的“快乐暑假”2016年暑期展演在河滨公园举行。",
                    "author": "",
                    "recUnit": "编辑部",
                    "contact": "",
                    "relDate": "2016-08-31",
                    "magaImgurl": "|/magazine/userfiles/files/mag/mgMagazine/2016/11/46.jpg",
                    "magaLogourl": "|/magazine/userfiles/files/mag/mgMagazine/2016/10/aaa(1).jpg",
                    "firstColumn": "青春在线",
                    "twoColumn": "刊中报",
                    "periodicalDate": "2016-08",
                    "state": "",
                    "periodical": "103",
                    "content": "<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">为了给小朋友们的暑期生活增添更多快乐的色彩，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">7</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">22</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">日，由共青团府谷县委主办的&ldquo;快乐暑假&rdquo;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">2016</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">年暑期展演在河滨公园举行。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">晚会上，来自小童星艺术学校的孩子们用精彩的舞蹈、悦耳的歌声吸引着观众的目光。舞蹈《向快乐出发》舞动着梦想的翅膀，唱出了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">00</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">后幸福的节奏；独舞《桃花》优美的舞姿让人仿佛置身于世外桃源，孩子们精彩的表演不时赢得在场观众的掌声和叫好声。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-font-kerning:1.0pt;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;\r\nmso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">最后，晚会在热情洋溢的《春牛呈祥》中落下了帷幕。整台晚会节目编排精美、引人入胜，内容丰富多彩、通俗易懂，以观众喜闻乐见的舞蹈、合唱等艺术形式将孩子们精湛的技艺，稚嫩的童声，优美的舞姿展现出来。本场晚会给了孩子们展示自我的机会，也为观众呈现了一场精彩的视觉盛宴。</span></p>",
                    "magaThumburl": "/magazine/userfiles/_thumbs/files/mag/mgMagazine/2016/08/46.jpg,",
                    "count": "",
                    "souCount": "",
                    "souName": "编辑部"
                },
                {
                    "id": "278",
                    "isNewRecord": false,
                    "remarks": "",
                    "createDate": "",
                    "updateDate": "",
                    "title": "“爱在人间”资助贫困文科状元上大学",
                    "summary": "8月14日，府谷县“爱在人间”志愿者协会一行，冒雨前往府谷县2016年文科状元郭永杰家中实地走访，并现场捐赠善款3000元。",
                    "author": "",
                    "recUnit": "编辑部",
                    "contact": "",
                    "relDate": "2016-08-31",
                    "magaImgurl": "",
                    "magaLogourl": "|/magazine/userfiles/files/mag/mgMagazine/2016/10/aaa(1).jpg",
                    "firstColumn": "青春在线",
                    "twoColumn": "刊中报",
                    "periodicalDate": "2016-08",
                    "state": "",
                    "periodical": "103",
                    "content": "<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">8</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">14</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">日，府谷县&ldquo;爱在人间&rdquo;志愿者协会一行，冒雨前往府谷县</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">2016</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">年文科状元郭永杰家中实地走访，并现场捐赠善款</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">3000</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">元。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">郭文杰在今年高考中以</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">602</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">分的高分夺得府谷县文科状元，并被吉林大学录取。郭文杰姐弟三人都在上大学，母亲患有腰腿疼痛疾病无法劳动，且长期需要药物维持，家中所有生计全靠父亲一人在外打工维持，生活极其困难。&ldquo;爱在人间&rdquo;志愿者协会知道后，纷纷献出一份爱心，帮助郭文杰度过难关。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">在郭文杰家里，志愿者们与他促膝谈心，详细了解他的学习、生活状况以及家庭经济情况，引导他树立积极向上的心态，增强求学的信心。当志愿者将爱心款送到郭文杰手中时，他激动地说着：&ldquo;谢谢，谢谢你们这些好心人</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">!</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">今后我要更加努力学习，尽自己最大努力去回报社会。&rdquo;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>",
                    "magaThumburl": "",
                    "count": "",
                    "souCount": "",
                    "souName": "编辑部"
                },
                {
                    "id": "279",
                    "isNewRecord": false,
                    "remarks": "",
                    "createDate": "",
                    "updateDate": "",
                    "title": "共青团定边县委开展2016YMCA 国际义工沙漠植树服务营活动",
                    "summary": "7月26日至7月30日由香港中华基督教青年会、西安市基督教青年会和定边团县委联合举办的“2016常青林义工沙漠植树服务营”在定边县举行。",
                    "author": "",
                    "recUnit": "编辑部",
                    "contact": "",
                    "relDate": "2016-08-31",
                    "magaImgurl": "|/magazine/userfiles/files/mag/mgMagazine/2016/11/47.jpg",
                    "magaLogourl": "|/magazine/userfiles/files/mag/mgMagazine/2016/10/aaa(1).jpg",
                    "firstColumn": "青春在线",
                    "twoColumn": "刊中报",
                    "periodicalDate": "2016-08",
                    "state": "",
                    "periodical": "103",
                    "content": "<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">7</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">26</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">日至</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">7</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">30</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">日由香港中华基督教青年会、西安市基督教青年会和定边团县委联合举办的&ldquo;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">2016</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">常青林义工沙漠植树服务营&rdquo;在定边县举行。活动期间，来自台湾、香港、澳门、天津、定边、韩国大邱、广州、西安等各地</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">100</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">余名青年义工在团县委组织协调下，先后深入到常青林植树基地及贺圈镇五兴庄村开展植树、固沙、打沙障活动，并举行各地义工环保演讲和团契活动。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">活动期间，义工开展了&ldquo;关爱留守儿童夏令日营服务活动&rdquo;，通过丰富多彩的室外集体游戏让小朋友们了解环保的重要性，树立团队协作精神，培养自信坚强的品格。学生们纷纷将自己制作的手工剪纸赠送给港澳台、韩国等地的青年义工们。这次活动使青年义工们之间增加了解、促进友谊、加强青年人关心他人、服务社会的意识，持续为环境保护做贡献。</span></p>",
                    "magaThumburl": "/magazine/userfiles/_thumbs/files/mag/mgMagazine/2016/08/47.jpg,",
                    "count": "",
                    "souCount": "",
                    "souName": "编辑部"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
