                    "remarks": "",
                    "createDate": "",
                    "updateDate": "",
                    "title": "我和狗狗有个约定",
                    "summary": "八月的北方，才一入秋，天气已经转凉。",
                    "author": "文/ 惠诗钦",
                    "recUnit": "青年服务中心",
                    "contact": "",
                    "relDate": "2016-08-31",
                    "magaImgurl": "|/magazine/userfiles/files/mag/mgMagazine/2016/10/14.jpg",
                    "magaLogourl": "|/magazine/userfiles/files/mag/mgMagazine/2016/10/aaa(1).jpg",
                    "firstColumn": "青春在线",
                    "twoColumn": "心灵家园",
                    "periodicalDate": "2016-08",
                    "state": "",
                    "periodical": "103",
                    "content": "<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">八月的北方，才一入秋，天气已经转凉。这是一场暴雨，昨晚下了一两小时，积水已经没到人的小腿，所幸黄土高原的地势很高，地下的沙土松软而吸水，抗洪能力极好。因此，这里不会像南方一样畏惧雨天。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">许是上天的恩赐吧，我坐月子的时间虽在数伏，然而天气却在一场又一场雨中出奇凉爽。直至立秋，火老虎刚来，炎热不过两天，就又迎来这场救命的暴雨。预报上说，这场雨会持续一周左右，除了对巷子外在建的工程有些许影响，对其他方面几乎没有影响。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">果不其然，才第二天清晨，雨停了一夜，天立马放晴。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">空气更不消说，简直清润得让人不忍形容。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">传说刚出月子的人是惧怕大太阳的，尤其是我这种尚有些爱美之心的女子。今天正是个好天气，尤其适合出行。尽管心里多少还抱着一些巷外的路会不会泥泞而不好前行的疑虑，不过出了门，在乎的就不那么多了，反而一点点淤泥更能激发起人想出去走走的决心。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">这是我出月子以来的第一次真正意义的出行，和平时怕着风着阳一出门就以车代步的感受完全不同。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">久居家中因休养生息而被幸福&ldquo;软禁&rdquo;出门，外面的世界何其新鲜，简直是有别于回忆的另一片天地。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">出了巷子，看到工程还在进展，并没有因为天气的影响而推延，这令我十分吃惊，实实地为市政的改建效率称好。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">大型的抓土机器一刻不停地运作着，将两旁土堆上的沙石铲起，重重地填补进前几天在路中挖好的大坑。如今那大坑中已埋好了线路和管道，填平沙土后做好路面、刷上沥青就要竣工了。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">若不是这次工程，我还从没有见过如此大的机器，高约四五层楼，装土的翻斗像挂在大机器上的勺子，一勺一勺地舀起泥土，又一勺一勺地倒进去。若是没有这机器，完全靠人力，完成这一系列的动作少说也得大半个下午，况且是重劳力，一般的人起码得用一天。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">机器轰轰隆隆地响着，运作着，看了一会儿后爱人就牵着我的手离开。本来我还想多看一会儿，但一想到，如今的我看什么都是风景，而这些并非所有都是常人眼里的风景，就跟着他，没有回头地离开了。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">由于工程的关系，巷外被一块一块的提示标牌分成不等的几份，那里是人行道、那里是停车区，一目了然。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">我们则沿着人行道走，细小的淤泥围成几条细小的河流，我们手牵手一一趟过。两旁的很多门面暂停营业，行人少了，吆喝声也少，让世界更加安静、返璞归真。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">或许此次出行没有任何目的地可说，我们只管顺着心情一路走。走到一处，开始回头。到底因为什么原因要往返，一时也说不清。途径小店，想到要带一份早点给家人，便随意停在一处。爱人进门点餐，我则停在门外，独自欣赏自己眼中的风景。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">这时，看到一侧走来的三只小狗，不经点起爱心，俯身去逗。那三只小狗样貌体态各异。领头的一只是黑白相间的中等大小的狗，看起来有点拉布拉多的样子，又不完全像。另外两只几乎并驾齐驱，一只是京巴大小的黄狗，另一只有点像牧羊犬，然而身材却小得多。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">可能是喂养过小狗的原因，我对他们的到来感到十分亲切。尤其是那只伪拉布拉多犬，长相可爱且温顺，特别讨我的喜欢。而且，这只狗狗在爱人缺席的时候竟一直安安静静地卧在脚旁，我见犹怜。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">我低头看着他，而那一刻，他恰巧也抬头看着我。目光相遇且相交。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">街上行人匆匆，他任何人也不追逐，唯独静静陪着我。先是动了动左耳，轻轻靠近我的小腿，见我向他笑了，继续动了动右耳更加表现出他的可爱。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">随后，爱人出来了，一手提着打包好的早点，另一手很自然地牵起我，&ldquo;宝宝，怎么不走啊？&rdquo;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">我的双脚像钉住一样，他拉我不动，于是问。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&ldquo;你看，你看，这些小狗。&rdquo;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&ldquo;一群流浪狗，没什么稀奇。&rdquo;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&ldquo;我不觉得啊，你看这只一直卧在我身边，这么久了。&rdquo;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&ldquo;喜欢？&rdquo;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">我没有出声，只是微笑着点点头。再看他的眼睛，满满地全是暖意。一则因为他也爱狗，二是因为他爱爱狗的女孩。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">然而理智告诉我，家中有嗷嗷待哺的小女儿，现在完全不是考虑养狗的时候，我甚至不敢蹲身下去摸一摸小狗的身体，怕有对宝宝不好的细菌。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">只好向前走。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">可那黑白小狗以及他的两个同伴却一直跟着我们的脚步，竟不像以前家里喂养过的其中一只狗狗，总是在我的前头大肆地奔跑，常常弄得我追赶不及她的脚步。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">这只狗狗很温顺，对我亦步亦趋，也离我最近。倒不像其他两只狗狗，仅远远地跟随。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">又走了一阵子，到了一个小商店门口。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&ldquo;宝宝稍等一下，我去买几根火腿。&rdquo;爱人对我说。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&ldquo;喂他们？&rdquo;问这话时，我眼中已激荡起一些幸福的涟漪。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">同样的场景将我带入对恋爱初期的回忆中，也是我们途遇小狗，也是类似的情景下，他跑进超市买火腿肠，让我在外边等候，然后我们一起蹲着给小狗喂食。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">那是我第一次看到对小动物如此好心的人，也因为那一刻，我对身边人的好感又多了一分。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&ldquo;是啊。&rdquo;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">他微笑着回答我。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">我亲昵地叫了一声&ldquo;老公&rdquo;，跟着他笑了起来。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">剥开火腿肠的外衣，我轻轻地将手中的食物扔在地上，一开始黑白狗狗还有一点拘谨，不敢低头去吃，后来扔得多了一些，他慢慢放开了，一块一块地将美味收入囊中。也开始对着我们摇尾巴，表达感激的心情。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">而他的两个同伴依然远远地观望着，不敢走近。眼看买来的食粮快要弹尽粮绝了，于是我将火腿也扔给另外两只狗狗的位置，可他们却仍不敢吃，只有这只黑白狗狗跑过去全吃掉了。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">就要过马路了，爱人说狗狗都惧怕车辆，让我把火腿扔得远一些，等他们去吃的时候，立马走过马路就可以轻松甩开他们了。这也是没有办法的办法。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">可接下来黑白狗狗的表现却着实让人意外，他从不回头寻任何一块扔过去的火腿肠，而是站在马路边，痴痴地看着我们。我和爱人趁着车少一溜烟跑过马路，想甩开狗狗，而她却在车辆突然多起来的时候仍然哒哒哒跑过来，对我们不离不弃。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">过了马路，三只狗狗只剩一只了。一路上黑白狗狗一直跟在我们身后，乖乖的，一点声音也不发出。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&ldquo;狗狗好可爱啊，若是以前&hellip;&hellip;&rdquo;&ldquo;以前的话我们就可以送他去宠物店洗得干干净净，然后抱回家养。&rdquo;爱人轻易地猜到了我的心思。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&ldquo;可是&hellip;&hellip;&rdquo;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&ldquo;可是现在有小楚楚，我们照顾不了他。&rdquo;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&ldquo;嗯嗯。&rdquo;我委屈地点点头。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">怕狗狗继续跟着，我和爱人又走进卖菜的小铁皮房子，主要为了离开狗狗的视线，顺便买买菜。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&ldquo;好久不见，恢复得不错啊，娃娃多少天了？&rdquo;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&ldquo;五十四天。&rdquo;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">许久不出门的我，一边挑菜一边和菜老板寒暄几句。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">出门时，心想狗狗一定去了别处吧，竟长长舒了一口气。而推开门，却看到狗狗蹲在门口，立起双耳摇着尾巴等候我们。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&ldquo;老公&hellip;&hellip;&rdquo;我一时没有了主意，只是感到惊愕。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&ldquo;真没想到狗狗居然还在。&rdquo;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&ldquo;是不是也多少动了一些恻隐之心啊？&rdquo;我进一步问道。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&ldquo;不动是不可能的，这么可爱的狗狗。&rdquo;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&ldquo;可是我们有小楚楚，现在不是养狗狗的时候。&rdquo;他叹了口气，低头看看狗狗，狗狗正好也看着他。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&ldquo;对啊，若是楚楚再大一些，两三岁了真的可以考虑考虑哦。&rdquo;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">我当然知道老公比我更爱狗，比我更想尽快给可爱的黑白狗狗一个归宿。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&ldquo;好吧，那我们就以三年为约，若狗狗还没有被人抱走，若狗狗还记得我们，认定我们是他的主人，那么我们就抱他回家。&rdquo;爱人坚定的表情，像是对我说又像是在给狗狗承诺。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&ldquo;图图。&rdquo;我突然这么叫他，大概是受了&ldquo;楚楚&rdquo;这个名字的启发。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">而他，居然站起身来，欢快地摇起了尾巴，并且轻轻地汪了一声，好像已经认定了这个称呼。那也是我第一次听到黑白狗狗的叫声，真的，很温柔，很好听。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&ldquo;那以后就依宝宝的，叫他&lsquo;图图&rsquo;&rdquo;。爱人如是说。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&ldquo;好啊，好啊，&rdquo;我开心地笑起来，有些乐不可支地说唱起来&ldquo;楚楚，图图，傻傻分不清楚。&rdquo;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&ldquo;嘿，小样。&rdquo;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">买完菜，就要进巷子了，去的时候还好好的，回来的时候竟发现巷子里也开始动工了，已经挖开一些了，泥土堆在两边，路很不好走。我突然开始担心，若图图走着走着，觉得路不好走，就不再跟随我们了，怎么办？</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">可转念一想，如若图图亦步亦趋地跟着我们回家，摆出各种可爱可怜状，让我们又心疼又心爱，不得不养怎么办？</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">被土土沙沙堆满的巷子确实不好走，爱人拉着我左拐右拐，好不容易到了大门口，要进院子了，图图依然形影不离。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">为了楚楚，我们实在没有能力喂养他。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&ldquo;那可怎么办啊？&rdquo;这是我惯用的一个句式，类似于口头禅，但此时确实表达出我左右为难的心情。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">爱人没有说话，也是静观其变的态度。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">后来狗狗一直随着我们走进院子，穿过一号楼、二号楼，直指家所在的三号楼。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">我回头看看爱人，眉头不由得向中间聚合了几下，有些不好抉择。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">爱人则低着头不说话。心里也没有确切的答案。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">只好硬着头皮上楼，我在前爱人在后，狗狗最后。他从来不和我们抢道，很有秩序感也很有礼貌。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">匆匆地登上二楼，这时正巧有几个人一齐下楼，一边聊着天声音很高，这让图图顿了一下，再也跟不上我们的步伐。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&ldquo;图图呢？&rdquo;已到四楼家门口的我，向下望，一边发问着。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&ldquo;可能下楼去了吧。&rdquo;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&ldquo;那他不跟随我们了吗？&rdquo;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&ldquo;估计不了吧，他朝下走了，回去了。&rdquo;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&ldquo;可是图图有家吗？&rdquo;我有点难掩哽咽地问道。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&ldquo;有，或者没有。&rdquo;爱人也实在给不了我一个确切的答案。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">是啊，图图有家或者没有家，似乎已经不再和我们相干，至少在他把我们认定是他的主人以后，我们却没有给他一个家，不是不想给，而是真的没有能力给。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">或许这些，图图并不能完全理解，他只能在与主人走散以后悻悻地下楼，觉得自己又遭到了一次遗弃。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">继续上路，流浪，永远没有尽头地流浪&hellip;&hellip;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">而我和爱人，却紧紧地记住了那个三年之约，希望那个约定有朝一日，可以真的实现。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>",
